GlobalVariables.StudyDescription: The discontinuation rate associated with this oral dosing regimen was 58.6% in previous studies, and alternative clinical strategies have been sought to improve tolerance for the compound. To that end, development of a Transdermal Therapeutic System (TTS) has been initiated.
